# Lesson: Verify Before Bulk Action

<!-- `lesson` type: a distilled, generalizable rule extracted from one or
     more incidents. Should read like a maxim — a sentence or two, not a
     case report. The full incident writeup belongs in a `feedback` file
     or LESSONS-LEARNED.md; this file is the compressed, durable takeaway. -->

## Current Conclusion

A broad instruction authorizes a category of action, not every specific
item it could match. Enumerate candidates and confirm before any action
that deletes, overwrites, or discards more than one item at once.

